Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:12.08,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Reincarnation and rebirth shroud love and hate in mist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:17.50,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}We were once acquainted and our azure swords crossed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:24.47,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}From the depths of the clouds flows a melody of zither and flute
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:29.82,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The physical realm is transient, like the drunken dream of a lone soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:33.99,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Overlooking both good and evil, I witness the chaos of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:36.07,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Side by side, we fight against the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:41.69,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Not once did I betray my principles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.74,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Leading a carefree life, I have transcended virtues and vices
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.46,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Yet I cannot erase the scars within my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:53.91,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}In this life, we shall not be caught in strife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.96,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Steering clear of worldly affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.54,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}we walk different paths while keeping justice in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:06.17,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I had been chivalrous and righteous, yet my deeds were all in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:10.01,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Good and evil are black and white
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.54,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}But the border between love and hate remains blurred
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:18.72,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Knowing you is like a dream
