Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:29.85,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Memories come back to me in the chilling winds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:35.85,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Engulfed by mist, I dispel the clouds only to perceive a fog
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:40.86,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I peer into the distance through the cold drizzle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:46.46,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Dusk has fallen, I cannot see the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:51.99,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I awake from the dream of my bloody past when I met my demise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:56.44,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Yet I do not blame my fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:59.86,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}In the boundless haze, good and evil walk separate paths
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:02.25,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I raise my wine cup as I weave a poem
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:06.16,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}My untamed heart will not be forsaken
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:09.24,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The strong gale blows against the tide
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:16.99,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Chaos rages around me, burying the past in the dust
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.80,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}I repeat to myself, "Keep justice in your heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:23.05,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The dauntless spirit of youth remains
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:27.46,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}The lingering melody of a flute relates my story
